{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "反常光譜", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "16-13", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "不曾遺忘", "storyInfo": "Mon3tr結束了變異裂獸的痛苦，三人決定回研究所。Mantra在村莊中確認了聖愚的存在，以及他與內衛之間的連繫。她似乎找到了打破困境的關鍵。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainlight_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g6_magnetofluidwaterfall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……;……", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line13", "option2": "line13"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "牠是不是……;不動了？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line15", "option2": "line15"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4208_wintim_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像……是這樣沒錯。", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#8$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吼聲，還有那種粗重的呼吸聲都消失了，是我們的攻擊對牠起作用了嗎？", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#8$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是牠還站著，沒有倒下——", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#8$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們先不要動！我過去看看。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#6$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "loop": "true", "channel": "w1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "w1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mon3tr確認兩人所在的位置安全後，獨自向前走去。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數秒前還無比癲狂的裂獸，此時已經被削去了部分體表的源石。牠異常安靜地站立著，就連奇怪的前肢也垂下，凝滯在身前。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mon3tr小心翼翼地朝牠靠近。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她觀察著這隻裂獸，原本危險的野獸，軀體上發生的畸變使牠的樣貌詭異萬分。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因為源石的影響，身體在急速向“人類”的方向轉變……", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#5$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定很痛苦吧……", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#5$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.6}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "Mon3tr，小心！;牠又動了！", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line45", "option2": "line45"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃——", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#8$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但預想中的攻擊並未發生。裂獸沒有移動，而是沉重地、毫無徵兆地向前倒下——"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_giantmonster_fall"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到牠的四肢重新接觸大地。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#9$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……Mon3tr，我認為我們應該趁這個機會離開。;離開這裡，回研究所。現在馬上。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line61", "option2": "line61"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，博士。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "Mon3tr？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line67"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 68, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_giantmonster_breathe"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠背上甚至還有起伏，牠還在呼吸！", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#8$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且牠聽起來……很痛苦？我不知道。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#5$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有阿米婭那種感受他人情緒的能力，更何況牠還只是一隻變異的動物，而且……", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#5$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道就算不管牠，把牠留在這裡，牠也會死。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#9$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石已經刺穿牠的喉嚨，牠全身沒有一處不痛，想把自己已經變異的器官都抓出來卻沒有能力。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#9$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許這也是為什麼之前牠會攻擊我們。牠沒辦法控制自己。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#9$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那就結束牠的痛苦吧。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line81"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#3$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沒錯。我能做到。我能……", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結束牠的痛苦。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "loop": "true", "channel": "w1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "w1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她繼續走向倒下的野獸，停在牠的近側，用爪子緊緊貼住一塊少有結晶的皮毛。"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mon3tr望著裂獸，打量牠的身體，眼底只有異樣的平靜。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，她以做微創手術般精準俐落的動作，掐滅了變異裂獸最後的、斷續的喘息。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$knifegore"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們走吧，博士。", "name": "Mon3tr"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回研究所。", "name": "Mon3tr"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "imgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$ib_screendistortion", "image": "66_i09"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra保持著聆聽狀態。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她深知自己視野中的景象已不再可信，無論它是遭到了有意的扭曲，還是意外地反映了真實。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是她聽著，直到人群之中，最後一句禱詞如同第一片雪花落下。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖愚……", "name": "Mantra"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“迦弗里伊爾”。", "name": "Mantra"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我在聽。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就停下來。", "name": "Mantra"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停止——", "name": "Mantra"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切！", "name": "Mantra"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我無權停止，因它從未開始。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你所見，只是你所想。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是Mantra不再嘗試溝通。她向前一步，試圖將那顫動著的紅、白、黑色線條穩定下來。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而就在她伸手的瞬間——"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "imgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……！", "name": "Mantra"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra——", "name": "忽近忽遠的聲音"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra！", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……什麼？", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#6$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才一動不動。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來都沒看過你這樣……你怎麼了？", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們沒有聽見嗎？", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#3$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽見什麼？", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#4$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年長的女人沒有立刻回答。"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她環視四周，發現留下的礦工姿態並不像先前那樣如出一轍。眼前的景象令她皺起眉頭，轉而看向自己身旁。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿洛伊澤在哪裡？", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#10$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她聽了我的話，跑出去了。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#3$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，至少你剛才確實有叫我們離開。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，但我一點也不記得我為什麼要叫你們離開……這太奇怪了。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "精神類源石技藝。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確定嗎？我們專門為此訓練過，如果受到這類攻擊，我不會毫無防備。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#4$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Raidian，檢查自己的短期記憶是否遭到了干擾。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#4$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪種干擾？", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#3$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能造成的干擾。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#4$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有次我讓Mechanist忘了去找你是要借用“小樹”和“小軸”的事，本質上不是抹除了那段記憶，而是阻斷了記憶的形成。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#4$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得……那是你第一次嘗試像這樣使用自己的源石技藝？大腦內的資訊沒有被成功儲存就會造成記憶缺失，也就是遺忘。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#4$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，來自你的提議。在對人體電訊號的瞭解和利用上，你比我更有經驗。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得這裡有人能跟你使用一樣的源石技藝？", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無法確定，也可能我只是比你們看到、聽到了更多。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼說？", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Raidian，烏薩斯的聖愚可能在這裡。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#4$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖愚？為什麼突然提起——", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#4$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖愚在這裡？但烏薩斯僅存的聖愚，兩年前就已經在聖駿堡被燒死了，這麼短的時間之內，有可能誕生另一個聖愚嗎？", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道。這是我接下來要去確認的。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果真的是聖愚，如果他隱藏在隊伍裡，一路上我卻什麼都沒發現……那就太危險了。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會讓其他人保持警戒，你也注意安全。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目前的危險不是物理上的，至少暫時不是。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果需要，我會及時求助。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘了。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#2$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra轉身，邁向數秒前那紅色曾經存在的位置。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "路上，不斷有擁擠著靠在一起的礦工為她讓出路來，或向她伸出了手。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，您想找……誰？", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還會，離開，去聖駿堡，對嗎？", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會，活、活下去……", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（點頭）", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們，好像，不想離開？我也問了，畢揚叔叔，他不想離開。", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他寧願，讓傷口，爛掉，也……不願再、再逃了。", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，活著……難道不比，其他所有事，都重要嗎？", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#2$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您，不說話……", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陌生人。", "name": "疲倦的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要去見娜迦，是不是？那你該膝行過去，仰著頭瞧她。", "name": "疲倦的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看著她，懺悔，然後得到寬恕。很快你就會發現從前不斷掙扎、始終無法得到平靜的自己，簡直就是愚蠢至極。", "name": "疲倦的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra不置可否。她沒有使用源石技藝與這些人對話，只是頷首，而後目不轉睛地盯著房間深處，與他們錯身。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會明白的……等到了她的跟前，你就會明白的。", "name": "疲倦的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屋內盡頭，在其他人眼中佝僂而渺小的灰白身影正靜靜坐著，彷彿一尊雕像。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g15_ursusvillage_ruins", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——聖愚？！", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#11$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不可能。絕不可能！聖愚已經死了！", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當初陛下出於仁慈，在定罪前允許那個瘋子為自己的罪行進行辯護。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果整整七天！整整七天他滴水未進，只為一刻不停地發表詭辯，拖延時間。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時他甚至還膽敢站在帝國議會的中央，對每一個走進來旁聽的人說——", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#5$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我原諒你”！", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#8$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後陛下忍無可忍，親自宣判了他的死刑，但仍有被他蠱惑的信眾去劫法場，進而爆發了近十年來發生在聖駿堡城區內最大的一場騷亂。", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#4$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的這些事我們都知道。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#3$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1966_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿洛伊澤"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1966_1#10$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問題在於，如果Mantra說那是聖愚，一定是因為對方露出了可供揣摩的痕跡。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要做的只是保護好自己，然後等待她的消息。", "name": "Raidian"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1730_1#5$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra並未像先前礦工說的那樣俯下身去。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她踏進背光的陰影裡，直視前方，彷彿眼前是一雙回望的眼瞳。"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，你能“聽見”。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$kjerag_n_intro", "key": "$kjerag_n_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我聽見，你飽含疑問。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你不是只會模仿我的源石技藝和說話方式，聖愚。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“聖愚”……如果你需要我是這個名字。", "name": "娜迦"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請解釋這句話的含義。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迦弗里伊爾、索洛米達、貝斯梅特、阿芙羅拉、娜迦……又或者，“聖愚”。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有這些，都是“我”。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……告訴我，你為什麼要混入這些受苦的人當中？", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為，這是一場佈道。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我將行遍這片廣袤的土地，為了贖去人們遭受的苦。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也因為，我看見了她，聽見了她。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為她的痛苦所挽留，也因此駐足。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“她”是誰？", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個受苦的靈魂。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你誘騙她，讓她稱你為“娜迦”？", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從未誘騙。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說謊。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她像你一樣提問，我像我一般回答。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅此而已。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有意義的回答。你到底是什麼？", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也看到我。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到無序的虛影。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我是。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但在其他人眼中，你不是。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解釋。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "世人看到的我的模樣，只反映了他們對我的認知和期待。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為，在所有靈魂當中，只有你會理解我為何如此存在。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟……", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是那個未完成的雕像，你曾會成為——", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我”。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra緊緊盯著眼前詭異的虛影，卻不確定自己能否從那上面看出任何有助於自己判斷的資訊。"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很久以前，你曾剝除過一塊黑色的腐肉。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也一樣。它追趕我，我驅逐它，像在呼吸之間從身上割下一塊腐肉。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒謬的比喻。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。這只是簡單的道理。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果它已經腐爛，不再與你身體的其他部分同氣連枝……", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那又為何還要保留？", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_29", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是……", "name": "Mantra"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i01", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的記憶？", "name": "Mantra"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i02", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i03", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但也是我——", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。內衛……你能影響內衛，你當然也能影響那些礦工。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#10$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你殺死它。你成為我。", "name": "娜迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#10$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這是我們之間唯一的共通點，那麼……", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“身體”、“腐肉”。你與內衛的關係——聖愚是內衛實驗的源頭。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#6$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從顫動著的虛影之中，不再有聲音傳來。既不辯駁，也不肯定。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra開始後退，離開了陰影的邊緣。"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……Raidian，我需要支援。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在。", "name": "Raidian"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已確認先前的推測。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，補充資訊……", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖愚隱藏在礦工之中，幫助他們殺死了內衛。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我明白了。", "name": "Raidian"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你需要我們怎麼做？", "name": "Raidian"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要你繼續想辦法聯絡羅德島在烏薩斯其他地區的支援隊伍，同時請阿米婭拖住阿洛伊澤。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在不能馬上離開這裡，至少在我找到能喚醒礦工們的辦法之前不行。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓極境留在我的源石技藝使用範圍之內，我可能會需要他的幫助。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想做什麼？", "name": "Raidian"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解除聖愚施加在礦工們身上的影響。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你認為是聖愚控制了這些礦工，讓他們拒絕離開？", "name": "Raidian"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們無法直接殺死聖愚，但他卻隨時可以殺死這裡的每一個人。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#4$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……也許阿米婭能幫忙。", "name": "Raidian"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許可以，但阿米婭並不瞭解聖愚。我不希望她一無所知地捲入其中。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖愚與我的能力很相似，這也是為什麼只有我能做出這樣的判斷。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他依靠他人的認知建立自身，我需要找到使他建立起“娜迦”這個身分的關鍵，然後才能解除聖愚施加的影響。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有懷疑的對象了。", "name": "Raidian"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒錯。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#2$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#9$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra將視線投向四周的礦工，最後落到正從自己身旁經過，走向聖愚的女孩身上。"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她茫然地呢喃著，惶惑而悲傷。"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4204_mantra_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是需要時間確認。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_4204_mantra_1#3$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}